						<summary>

						<p>This inscription is in verse composed in <hi rend="italic">nērisai veṇbā</hi> metre. It registers a gift of 1000 <hi rend="italic">kuḻi</hi> of land at Kaḍalūr to the temple of Akkiyāṇḍār for performing morning service by the poet Agaḷaṅgaṉ.</p>						

